Showcasing his wares, Sunderland explains why and how they can change the situation for parents: “These handsets just make voice calls. There’s no screen and there’s no conventional keypad, so for instance you can’t access the internet, you can’t text, and problems like inappropriate access to websites, sexting, bullying by texting, those issues completely go away because the phone just makes calls.”
